Package: tndata
Title: Fetch Datasets from the Official Tunisian Data Catalog
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Aymen", "Nasri", , "aymennasrii@proton.me", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Simplifies access to Tunisian government open data from <https://data.gov.tn/fr/>.
      Queries datasets by theme, author, or keywords, retrieves metadata, and gets structured results ready for analysis; all through the official 'CKAN' API.
License: Apache License (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    dplyr,
    fs,
    glue,
    httr,
    httr2,
    jsonlite,
    logger,
    lubridate,
    purrr,
    stringr
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
URL: https://github.com/aymennasri/tndata, http://aymennasri.me/tndata/
BugReports: https://github.com/aymennasri/tndata/issues
